Product Description
A multi-million pound trust fund....a sexy MI5 spy at my side....a collection of Killer Louboutins...

Life in Chelsea was good.

But then Johnny asked me to kill a fat Russian mobster on the flight from Dubai....I got away with it....then he had me kill an East-End Rapper and I found myself framed for murder. Setup. We set off across Europe to find Johnny and get my money back, but with everyone from the Russian Mob to annoying French policemen trying to stop us, the only thing higher than my shopping bill at Gucci was the body count.
